description: This truck is quite the delightful sight on the streets of Buffalo, New York. And it’s not just because of its gorgeous design - it also undoubtedly guarantees that you’re about to dine on delicious gourmet Asian cuisine. Offering all your favorite foods with a flair, this truck's options include Fresh Roasted Broccoli Salad, Five-Spiced Sesame Chicken, and Spicy Peanut Butter Noodles, just to name a few. You are going to adore, and inevitably crave more of the fantastic fusion fare from Gourm-Asian Bistro!
name: The Gourm-Asian Bistro
